TITLE: Accessing Session in Next.js Server Component
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to fetch and use session data in a Next.js server component to display a user avatar.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nextauthjs/next-auth/blob/main/docs/pages/getting-started/session-management/get-session.mdx#2025-04-12_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
```
import { auth } from "../auth"

export default async function UserAvatar() {
  const session = await auth()

  if (!session?.user) return null

  return (
    <div>
      <img src={session.user.image} alt="User Avatar" />
    </div>
  )
}
```

