TITLE: Configuring Auth.js v5 for Edge Compatibility in Next.js
DESCRIPTION: This set of snippets demonstrates how to configure Auth.js v5 for edge compatibility in Next.js. It shows how to split the configuration into multiple files to ensure edge compatibility while still using database adapters.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nextauthjs/next-auth/blob/main/docs/pages/getting-started/migrating-to-v5.mdx#2025-04-12_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: typescript
