TITLE: Creating Neo4j Single-Property Indexes for Community Edition
DESCRIPTION: SQL commands to create single-property indexes specifically for Neo4j Community Edition to optimize Auth.js queries for accounts and verification tokens.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nextauthjs/next-auth/blob/main/docs/pages/getting-started/adapters/neo4j.mdx#2025-04-12_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: sql
CODE:
```
CREATE INDEX account_provider_index IF NOT EXISTS
FOR (a:Account) ON (a.provider);

CREATE INDEX account_provider_account_id_index IF NOT EXISTS
FOR (a:Account) ON (a.providerAccountId);

CREATE INDEX verification_token_identifier_index IF NOT EXISTS
FOR (v:VerificationToken) ON (v.identifier);

CREATE INDEX verification_token_token_index IF NOT EXISTS
FOR (v:VerificationToken) ON (v.token);
```

