TITLE: Configuring Supabase Adapter in SvelteKit
DESCRIPTION: This code demonstrates how to set up the Supabase adapter in a SvelteKit application using Auth.js.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nextauthjs/next-auth/blob/main/docs/pages/getting-started/adapters/supabase.mdx#2025-04-12_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import { SvelteKitAuth } from "@auth/sveltekit"
import { SupabaseAdapter } from "@auth/supabase-adapter"

export const { handle, signIn, signOut } = SvelteKitAuth({
  providers: [],
  adapter: SupabaseAdapter({
    url: process.env.SUPABASE_URL,
    secret: process.env.SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY,
  }),
})
```

