TITLE: Configuring Unstorage Adapter in Qwik
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet shows how to configure the Unstorage adapter in a Qwik application using QwikAuth$. It sets up the storage and configures the adapter.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nextauthjs/next-auth/blob/main/docs/pages/getting-started/adapters/unstorage.mdx#2025-04-12_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import { QwikAuth$ } from "@auth/qwik"
import { UnstorageAdapter } from "@auth/unstorage-adapter"
import { createStorage } from "unstorage"

const storage = createStorage()

export const { onRequest, useSession, useSignIn, useSignOut } = QwikAuth$(
  () => ({
    providers: [],
    adapter: UnstorageAdapter(storage),
  })
)
```

