TITLE: Adding CharacterID to JWT and Session in EVEOnline Authentication
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to add the CharacterID from the EVEOnline profile to the JWT and session. This is useful when using JWT for session management.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nextauthjs/next-auth/blob/main/docs/pages/getting-started/providers/eveonline.mdx#2025-04-12_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: ts
CODE:
```
const AuthConfig = {
  callbacks: {
    jwt({ token, profile }) {
      if (profile) {
        token.characterId = profile.CharacterID
      }
      return token
    },
    session({ session, token }) {
      session.user.characterId = token.characterId
      return session
    },
  },
}
```

